{
  "page": "Bellonara Otherys",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the eldest bastard daughter of King Aegon IV Targaryen by Bellegere Otherys, see <a href=\"/index.php/Bellenora_Otherys\" title=\"Bellenora Otherys\">Bellenora Otherys</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\"><img alt=\"Braavos.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/50px-Braavos.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/75px-Braavos.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/100px-Braavos.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Bellonara Otherys</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\"><img alt=\"Braavos.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/50px-Braavos.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/75px-Braavos.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/100px-Braavos.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Bellonara_Otherys.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Bellonara Otherys.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/81/Bellonara_Otherys.png/350px-Bellonara_Otherys.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"394\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/81/Bellonara_Otherys.png/525px-Bellonara_Otherys.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/81/Bellonara_Otherys.png/700px-Bellonara_Otherys.png 2x\" /></a><div>Bellonara Otherys, generated with Stable Diffusion</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Black_Pearl_of_Braavos\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Black Pearl of Braavos\">Black Pearl of Braavos</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Otherys\" title=\"House Otherys\">House Otherys</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavosi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Bellegere_Otherys_(courtesan)\" title=\"Bellegere Otherys (courtesan)\">Bellegere Otherys</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table> \n<p><b>Bellonara Otherys</b>, once the Black Pearl of Braavos, is the mother of <a href=\"/index.php/Bellegere_Otherys_(Courtesan)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bellegere Otherys (Courtesan)\">Bellegere Otherys</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Courtesan\" title=\"Courtesan\">courtesan</a> who is currently called the <a href=\"/index.php/Black_Pearl_of_Braavos\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Black Pearl of Braavos\">Black Pearl</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bellonara_Otherys&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Bellonara had been the <a href=\"/index.php/Black_Pearl_of_Braavos\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Black Pearl of Braavos\">Black Pearl of Braavos</a> before her daughter, <a href=\"/index.php/Bellegere_Otherys_(Courtesan)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bellegere Otherys (Courtesan)\">Bellegere</a>. Bellonara had succeeded the position from her own mother, who had been a Black Pearl as well, and whose own mother, in turn, had been a Black Pearl too.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bellonara_Otherys&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Bellonara can trace her descent through the female line to the daughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Bellegere_Otherys\" title=\"Bellegere Otherys\">Bellegere Otherys</a>, a pirate queen who was the first Black Pearl, and King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_IV_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon IV Targaryen\">Aegon IV Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Sealord\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sealord\">Sealord<br />Otherys</a></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"wi